# Project Specification & Guidelines

Use the project specification and guidelines to build the Todo app.

## Overview

Commanders-log is a web app that allows users to record their notes, upload audio recordings, videos, and image files, and generate summaries of their activities.

## Tech Stack

- Frontend: React, TypeScript, TailwindCSS
- Backend: FastAPI, SQLite, SQLAlchemy, Pydantic
- Auth: Clerk
- Payments: Stripe

